claim.claim-text:
A control device of an electrically operated valve having an inflow port and an outflow port of a fluid, a valve body which controls a flow rate of the fluid flowing out of said outflow port, and a motor which drives said valve body, the control device comprising:
a valve opening degree control means which controls a valve opening degree of said electrically operated valve;
an initializing control means which executes an initializing process of said electrically operated valve; and
a memory means;
wherein said memory means stores an executing frequency of an initializing process.
